> 
> peak memory: 2076.94 MiB, increment: 360.37 MiB
> CPU times: user 6min 5s, sys: 236 ms, total: 6min 5s

However, this solution seems difficult in cross-validation. Do you have any suggestion? Maybe using `itertools.tee`?

